<br>
Go into the game and think of everything as new.  That person named Seinfeld is the only person named Sienfeld that you have ever met.  Don't expect him to be Jerry Sienfeld from TV.  Don't put that stipulation on him or her for that matter.   Don't look at Compton and say damn thats a gangland area in CA.  Say wow thats a big city run by an evil guild in Aerynth.<br>
<br>
